Class DynamicList<T>

java.lang.Object
  ikor.collection.DynamicList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<T>, List<T>, MutableCollection<T>, MutableList<T>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class DynamicList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MutableList<T>

Standard dynamic list implementation, based on java.util.ArrayList (not-synchronized resizable-array implementation in the Java Collections Framework).

Author:
Fernando Berzal
